        <p><strong>Location:</strong> Federal Court of Canada at 701 West Georgia Street, Vancouver, in courtroom 701.</p>
        <p><strong>Visual/Audio Opportunity:</strong> Commissioner Cullen will make introductory remarks at the outset of the hearing. There will be the opportunity to videotape and take photos during Commissioner Cullen’s opening remarks in the courtroom. At the conclusion of the Commissioner’s opening remarks, there will be a two-minute break and media will be asked to end videotaping and photography. The hearing will then begin.</p>
